Installation
---------------------------------------------------------------------
To install apertium-morph you need a Java 1.5 (or higher) compiler and
Apache Lucene (http://lucene.apache.org/) then you need to uncompress
apertium-morph in the 'contrib' folder on lucene and run ant:

$ cd contrib
$ tar xvfz apertium-morph.tgz
$ cd apertium-morph
$ ant


Each Java class is properly documented, if you want to build the
documentation run:

$ ant javadocs

You also need to install apertium and lttoolbox, you will find both
packages availalbe at http://sourceforge.net/projects/apertium/.

